dc_title_s: Geologic map and cross section of Ohio
dc_description_s: "Publication date: 11/2001."|Cross section color-coded for geologic time period represented within the geologic layers.|Includes notes, color cross-section, and logos for the Dept. of Natural Resources and the Geological Survey.|Scale approximately 1:2,100,000.|Also shows the terminal glacial boundary.|State of Ohio, Department of Natural Resources, Division of Geological Survey.
